---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about DeML OS - an open, research-oriented effort for decentralized machine learning systems">
  <section class="py-12 lg:py-20">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <header class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About DeML OS</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          An open, research-oriented effort to define the system layer for decentralized machine learning.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose-custom mb-16">
        <p>
          We are not building a single product. We are working on shared abstractions, 
          evaluation frameworks, and system understanding for the emerging field of 
          decentralized machine learning.
        </p>
        <p>
          The intersection of Web3 and AI presents fundamental questions about how 
          machine learning can be executed, verified, settled, and constrained without 
          relying on central platforms. These questions require rigorous technical 
          analysis, not marketing narratives.
        </p>
        <p>
          DeML OS serves as a neutral ground for researchers, engineers, and practitioners 
          to explore these questions together, sharing knowledge and building common 
          understanding of the technical landscape.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="lucide:target" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" />
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            To provide objective, technical analysis of decentralized ML systems. 
            We evaluate projects on their technical merits, not their marketing or 
            token performance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent-100 dark:bg-accent-900/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="lucide:book-open" class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400" />
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Research Focus</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            We track developments in execution, verification, economics, and governance 
            of decentralized ML systems, maintaining a high-signal research log for 
            the community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="lucide:code" class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" />
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Open Source</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            All our research, frameworks, and tools are open source. We believe in 
            building public goods for the decentralized ML ecosystem.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="lucide:globe" class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400" />
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Neutral Ground</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            We are not affiliated with any specific project. Our goal is comparison 
            and understanding, not promotion or competition.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Who Should Join</h2>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">
            If you are interested in any of the following areas, you are welcome to join the discussion:
          </p>
          <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-500"></div>
              <span>Distributed systems</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-500"></div>
              <span>Machine learning systems</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-500"></div>
              <span>Verifiable computation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-500"></div>
              <span>Zero-knowledge proofs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-500"></div>
              <span>Crypto-economic mechanisms</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-500"></div>
              <span>Blockchain infrastructure</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-500"></div>
              <span>GPU/TPU hardware</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-500"></div>
              <span>Protocol design</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">How to Contribute</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="card p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Submit Research Notes</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
              Found an interesting paper, release, or discussion? Submit it for inclusion 
              in our research log. We review all submissions for relevance and quality.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Project Updates</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
              Working on a project we cover? Help us keep information accurate by 
              submitting updates or corrections through our GitHub repository.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Join Discussions</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
              Participate in technical discussions on our Telegram, Discord, or GitHub. 
              We welcome diverse perspectives and constructive debate.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Contact & Community</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <a 
            href="https://t.me/demlos" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="card p-6 text-center group hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 transition-colors"
          >
            <Icon name="lucide:send" class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-3 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors" />
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Telegram</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">@demlos</p>
          </a>

          <a 
            href="https://discord.gg/demlos" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="card p-6 text-center group hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 transition-colors"
          >
            <Icon name="lucide:message-circle" class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-3 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors" />
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Discord</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">discord.gg/demlos</p>
          </a>

          <a 
            href="https://github.com/demlos" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="card p-6 text-center group hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-700 transition-colors"
          >
            <Icon name="lucide:github" class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-3 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors" />
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">GitHub</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">github.com/demlos</p>
          </a>

          <div class="card p-6 text-center">
            <Icon name="lucide:users" class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-3 text-slate-400" />
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">WeChat</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Contact for invite</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
